{"tid":2346337,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅冠聰：【美國戰線 | 逾四百史丹福校友師生聯署 促保留校內唯一廣東話課程】","createTime":"2020-12-30T07:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T09:45:43.000Z","uid":210140,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a6c76bdaad5e80595cf707379cd777285b348664","tid":2346337,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T07:42:03.000Z","msg":"轉自Facebook<br />\n<br />\n在全面威權時代下，除了遊說各國警剔中共威脅外，亦要守護香港文化。美國史丹福大學早前以「削減開支」為由，拒絕向校內唯一廣東話課程教師張錫莉續約，令人擔心這個自1997年起設立的廣東話課程就此結束。<br />\n一班來自香港及海外的史丹福校友及畢業生隨即發起聯署，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">批評校方決定抹殺學校的多元價值政策，無視早年來自廣東的鐵路工人對學校創辦人利蘭史丹福鐵路事業的貢獻，亦忽視廣東話廣受海外離散華人所使用</span></strong></span>。聯署要求校方承諾每學期至少開辦一節廣東話課程，並開設永久全職教席，去確保廣東話課程繼續營運下去。<br />\n419名史丹福校友、職工及學生參與相關聯署，當中大部分持外國國藉。同時，聯署信得到300多名從事亞洲研究或亞美研究的學者及研究員所支持。<br />\n為了繼續存承香港人的文化素養，希望各位與史丹福大學有關的朋友都支持這個聯署。<br />\n聯署頁面<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScHwEw8KGfyCRrbY70oy1eSkTqal6DK9ed1JlJd7-pzJS2kZQ/viewform?fbclid=IwAR2rGrj2ca8iOOfKXUP5UKp-cJL6RqE_eAGEfntjD1J1oPuGZzbeQnQ5GgY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScHwEw8KGfyCRrbY70oy1eSkTqal6DK9ed1JlJd7-pzJS2kZQ%2Fviewform%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2rGrj2ca8iOOfKXUP5UKp-cJL6RqE_eAGEfntjD1J1oPuGZzbeQnQ5GgY&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSHdT8yuj5BXRLHKnqfTXFLo%3D&h=0b70024e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScHwEw8KGfyCRrbY70oy1eSkTqal6DK9ed1JlJd7-pzJS2kZQ/viewform?fbclid=IwAR2rGrj2ca8iOOfKXUP5UKp-cJL6RqE_eAGEfntjD1J1oPuGZzbeQnQ5GgY</a><br />\n聯署信正文<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1evpG5yTTJK3skdHSosminkGEB-v1EcN5HQEnkFjqQ-M/mobilebasic?fbclid=IwAR3vOBEmNVVsGAvkPQo6Dtr29yT9EswD_MiJALMUID1WXANH-NBXDbDlj30#h.ps5fxx702891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1evpG5yTTJK3skdHSosminkGEB-v1EcN5HQEnkFjqQ-M%2Fmobilebasic%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3vOBEmNVVsGAvkPQo6Dtr29yT9EswD_MiJALMUID1WXANH-NBXDbDlj30%23h.p